            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "additional note:\nif we want to move towards a minibuffer implementation then the current ui2 implementation of msg target is not good enough. if msg target is set to cmd then new messages while the minibuffer is in use will try to access the same space. so either the msg target needs to be adjusted or temporarily changed when the minibuffer is 'active' or the cmd target can never be cmd.",
